{"tid":1845700,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【預言】2011年電影《Contagion世紀戰疫》講述一隻蝙蝠同一隻豬引發全球大瘟疫","createTime":"2020-01-27T09:57:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-31T22:58:56.000Z","uid":48040,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"bf0001c0a6324db3a46a520680f5c724a1eb22bc","tid":1845700,"uid":48040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T09:57:25.000Z","msg":"電影講述瘟疫的起源：<br />\n<br />\n1、香港發展商為了建屋，推倒了成片樹林<br />\n2、原本棲息係度的蝙蝠無家可歸，四處飛<br />\n3、一隻蝙蝠飛過養豬場，掉下口中未食完的果實<br />\n4、一隻豬食咗蝙蝠咬過的果實<br />\n5、呢隻豬被賣到澳門的酒店，大廚準備做成燒豬<br />\n6、這時，waiter同大廚話外面有個鬼婆好欣賞你的手藝，想同你合照<br />\n7、大廚很開心即刻出去，他雙手有豬的鮮血，於是他隨便在圍裙上擦拭幾下就算<br />\n8、大廚與鬼婆握手，於是鬼婆就感染到蝙蝠的病毒<br />\n9、鬼婆回到美國，成為超級傳播者<br />\n<br />\n電影簡介（殘體字及強國話注意）：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rhxLyCMKZ4g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DrhxLyCMKZ4g&d=FyFnEhDp3tEmtF3AT420Rm6H7LaHGbUBdoVXdg05ZHE%3D&h=3e555447\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rhxLyCMKZ4g</a><br />\n<br />\nBTW，原來蝙蝠係飛行中的體溫達到40度，因此蝙蝠身上存活的病毒係40度都仍然相當活躍。"},{"pid":"7609ecfae7a86a97193bfaa3f0ca27c3cbc9261b","tid":1845700,"uid":315299,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T09:59:24.000Z","msg":"真定假, 求fc<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c4628e9a1510061cf1ad10427d4be3cce4f41af","tid":1845700,"uid":168267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T10:00:46.000Z","msg":"IMDB得6.6分<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d71f19d6d2efd50edbd4f9541ded1f9a1041c5ed","tid":1845700,"uid":194325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T10:01:16.000Z","msg":"￼大家可以幫手推post嗎？<br />\n<br />\n拜托請幫幫手，謝謝！<br />\n<br />\n香港金融業職工共同抗疫意見調查<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1843747\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1843747</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"248c54ae65c8e7537d721d95618e8b91b2e79da2","tid":1845700,"uid":48040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7c4628e9a1510061cf1ad10427d4be3cce4f41af","tid":1845700,"uid":168267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T10:00:46.000Z","msg":"IMDB得6.6分<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T10:02:20.000Z","msg":"嗰時未有武漢肺炎嘛。<br />\n呢部電影都講官員點樣輕視，結果導致疫情不可收拾。"},{"pid":"38c2ffa6edcd9cd7d2b394e42d9f100d4ab2dc19","tid":1845700,"uid":223987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T10:02:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一爆出黎都諗起呢套野"},{"pid":"8c8e6bdfa6bc07640c7340ffc30d96b26f6abf18","tid":1845700,"uid":37427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T10:11:07.000Z","msg":"睇過，算好睇"},{"pid":"8c8e40abfd96cf14077bd59232fe50faa442e06d","tid":1845700,"uid":37528,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T10:12:44.000Z","msg":"呢套唔係base on沙士咩？"},{"pid":"1e7e5c814be61788d42ed975bff3b36c2f941ebc","tid":1845700,"uid":7903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8c8e40abfd96cf14077bd59232fe50faa442e06d","tid":1845700,"uid":37528,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T10:12:44.000Z","msg":"呢套唔係base on沙士咩？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T10:16:04.000Z","msg":"當年拍丫嗎，緊係睇沙士"},{"pid":"63a2e531636984a158fc244c0a0038591a3993ff","tid":1845700,"uid":264755,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T10:16:12.000Z","msg":"呢套麻麻地，雖然粒粒星<br />\n泡菜國果套戰疫先癲<br />\n佢個故事個原形係sars加強版<br />\n因為有強國人偷渡去南韓傳左過去<br />\n由隔離去到封城再去到屠殺懷疑患者<br />\n最後出埋空軍想炸城<br />\n以前睇覺得好撚誇張<br />\n而家真係當預言片咁睇"},{"pid":"56aa48c37b15da57b1d2764a82a595f3a982986c","tid":1845700,"uid":53922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T12:14:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=V1HH1-ozS_A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DV1HH1-ozS_A&d=FyFnEhDp3tEmtF